{
  "stem": "1826.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also somehow she, she liked me-- how to say it-- liked me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How she was very sympathetic, very understanding to the situation and tried to, to show it any way she could.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And also offered me food and said anytime way I can come, I should come to her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the situation-- and they created a ghetto, a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the situation was worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tell us about conditions in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the conditions of the ghetto are, are disastrous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, there was no food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was hunger.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And secondly, they-- nobody knew what can happen to him today or tomorrow, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The rumors started, they liquidated the ghetto in another town, another city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was only by rumors, only by rumors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only by from, from the outside, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These people, the Ukrainian, the Gen-- they could travel, and they brought news, information about that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the situation was very, very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember one day I met near-- there was like a university, a [? liceum. ?] The name of Polish was [POLISH], [? liceum. ?] And I met this Maria Nikitichna, this Russian woman, and she said-- she told me there are rumors that something very bad is going to happen to the Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I told her, and I have a joking way, because I was so desperate, you know, so that I said to her, you know there is a saying in the Polish language.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whatever happens to the Jews might as well happen to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then she said, no, you shouldn't say it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We should try to do something about you, to, to save you, to save you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she told me if anything happens, I should come to her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she'll help me.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
